#: ../../desktop/macosvfs.rst:3
msgid "macOS Virtual Files Client"
msgstr "Cliant Comhad Fíorúil macOS"

#: ../../desktop/macosvfs.rst:5
msgid ""
"On macOS, our client can also seamlessly integrate Nextcloud files into "
"macOS as a file provider extension. Any newly configured Nextcloud account "
"will have the integration enabled by default."
msgstr ""
"Ar macOS, is féidir lenár gcliaint comhaid Nextcloud a chomhtháthú go gan "
"uaim i macOS mar shíneadh soláthraí comhad. Beidh an comhtháthú cumasaithe "
"de réir réamhshocraithe ar aon chuntas Nextcloud atá cumraithe as an nua."

#: ../../desktop/macosvfs.rst:10
msgid "Supported features"
msgstr "Gnéithe tacaithe"

#: ../../desktop/macosvfs.rst:12
msgid "Keeping files or whole folders available offline"
msgstr "Comhaid nó fillteáin iomlána a choinneáil ar fáil as líne"

#: ../../desktop/macosvfs.rst:13
msgid ""
"Freeing up local disk space by evicting local copies without deleting items"
msgstr ""
"Spás diosca áitiúil a shaoradh trí chóipeanna áitiúla a dhíbirt gan míreanna"
" a scriosadh"

#: ../../desktop/macosvfs.rst:14
msgid "Intelligent and automatic local data eviction"
msgstr "Díbirt sonraí áitiúla cliste agus uathoibríoch"

#: ../../desktop/macosvfs.rst:15
msgid "File previews within Finder for files which are not downloaded yet"
msgstr ""
"Réamhamhairc chomhaid laistigh den Aimsitheoir le haghaidh comhad nach "
"bhfuil íoslódáilte fós"

#: ../../desktop/macosvfs.rst:16
msgid ""
"Support for Apple-specific formats, for example Pages, Numbers or Keynote "
"bundles"
msgstr ""
"Tacaíocht do fhormáidí sonracha Apple, mar shampla pacáistí Pages, Numbers "
"nó Keynote"

#: ../../desktop/macosvfs.rst:17
msgid ""
"Support for server-side file locking (if supported by the connected server)"
msgstr ""
"Tacaíocht do ghlasáil comhad taobh an fhreastalaí (má thacaíonn an "
"freastalaí ceangailte leis)"

#: ../../desktop/macosvfs.rst:18
msgid "“Edit locally” support"
msgstr "Tacaíocht “Cuir in eagar go háitiúil”."

#: ../../desktop/macosvfs.rst:19
msgid "Sharing with other users"
msgstr "Ag roinnt le húsáideoirí eile"

#: ../../desktop/macosvfs.rst:20
msgid "Server-side actions integrated directly in Finder's context menu"
msgstr ""
"Gníomhartha taobh an fhreastalaí comhtháite go díreach i roghchlár "
"comhthéacs an Aimsitheora"

#: ../../desktop/macosvfs.rst:21
msgid "Automatic discovery of server-side changes"
msgstr "Aimsiú uathoibríoch ar athruithe taobh an fhreastalaí"

#: ../../desktop/macosvfs.rst:24
msgid "Configuration"
msgstr "Cumraíocht"

#: ../../desktop/macosvfs.rst:26
msgid ""
"Virtual files-related settings can be adjusted on a per-account basis via "
"the Nextcloud desktop client's settings window."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir socruithe a bhaineann le comhaid fhíorúla a choigeartú ar bhonn "
"cuntais aonair trí fhuinneog socruithe chliaint deisce Nextcloud."

#: ../../desktop/macosvfs.rst:29
msgid "Screenshot of client settings for the file provider extension"
msgstr "Scáileán de shocruithe cliant don síneadh soláthraí comhaid"

#: ../../desktop/macosvfs.rst:32
msgid "Here the integration into Finder can be enabled or disabled."
msgstr ""
"Anseo is féidir an comhtháthú isteach i Finder a chumasú nó a dhíchumasú."

#: ../../desktop/macosvfs.rst:34
msgid ""
"When disabling the file provider extension while still having unsynchronized"
" changes, macOS will save the unsynchronized items in a folder that is "
"automatically revealed after the integration is disabled."
msgstr ""
"Agus síneadh an tsoláthraí comhad á dhíchumasú agus athruithe "
"neamhshioncrónaithe fós ann, sábhálfaidh macOS na míreanna "
"neamhshioncrónaithe i bhfillteán a nochtar go huathoibríoch tar éis an "
"chomhtháthú a dhíchumasú."

#: ../../desktop/macosvfs.rst:39
msgid "Finder integration"
msgstr "Comhtháthú aimsitheoir"

#: ../../desktop/macosvfs.rst:41
msgid ""
"On macOS, remote storage like a Nextcloud files account appears like a "
"dedicated location in the Finder sidebar. The actual location of the content"
" on disk is defined by macOS."
msgstr ""
"Ar macOS, feictear stóráil iargúlta cosúil le cuntas comhad Nextcloud mar "
"shuíomh tiomnaithe i mbarra taoibh Finder. Sainmhíníonn macOS suíomh iarbhír"
" an ábhair ar an diosca."

#: ../../desktop/macosvfs.rst:45
msgid "Finder sidebar showing a Nextcloud file provider domain"
msgstr ""
"Barra taoibh aimsitheora a thaispeánann fearann ​​soláthraí comhad Nextcloud"

#: ../../desktop/macosvfs.rst:49
msgid ""
"To accelerate server-side change detection, we recommend enabling the "
"``notify_push`` app on your Nextcloud server. This app will notify the "
"desktop client of changes on the server as soon as they happen, reducing the"
" time it takes for changes to appear in Finder. Otherwise the client needs "
"to poll the server which will result in an increased delay between a change "
"on the server and its local visibility."
msgstr ""
"Chun braiteadh athruithe ar thaobh an fhreastalaí a bhrostú, molaimid an aip"
" ``notify_push`` a chumasú ar do fhreastalaí Nextcloud. Cuirfidh an aip seo "
"an cliant deisce ar an eolas faoi athruithe ar an bhfreastalaí a luaithe a "
"tharlaíonn siad, rud a laghdóidh an t-am a thógann sé chun athruithe a "
"bheith le feiceáil in Finder. Seachas sin, caithfidh an cliant suirbhé a "
"dhéanamh ar an bhfreastalaí rud a fhágfaidh go mbeidh moill mhéadaithe idir "
"athrú ar an bhfreastalaí agus a infheictheacht áitiúil."

#: ../../desktop/macosvfs.rst:57
msgid "Sync status indicators"
msgstr "Sioncronaigh táscairí stádais"

#: ../../desktop/macosvfs.rst:59
msgid ""
"Similar to classic synchronization folders, Finder displays status "
"indicators next to items. Unlike the custom indicators in classic "
"synchronization folders, these standardized indicators are provided by macOS"
" to ensure a consistent appearance across all cloud storage apps which a "
"user may use on their system."
msgstr ""
"Cosúil le fillteáin shioncrónaithe clasaiceacha, taispeánann Finder táscairí"
" stádais in aice le míreanna. Murab ionann agus na táscairí saincheaptha i "
"bhfillteáin shioncrónaithe clasaiceacha, soláthraíonn macOS na táscairí "
"caighdeánaithe seo chun cuma chomhsheasmhach a chinntiú ar fud na n-aip "
"stórála scamall go léir a d'fhéadfadh úsáideoir a úsáid ar a gcóras."

#: ../../desktop/macosvfs.rst:65
msgid ""
"*Cloud with downward arrow*: The item and its descendants are not downloaded"
" yet. They can be downloaded, assuming a network connection is available."
msgstr ""
"*Scamall le saighead anuas*: Níl an mhír ná a sliocht íoslódáilte fós. Is "
"féidir iad a íoslódáil, ar choinníoll go bhfuil nasc líonra ar fáil."

#: ../../desktop/macosvfs.rst:67
msgid ""
"*Outlined cloud*: The item is not fully uploaded yet in its current local "
"state."
msgstr ""
"*Scamall imlíneach*: Níl an mhír uaslódáilte go hiomlán fós ina staid "
"áitiúil reatha."

#: ../../desktop/macosvfs.rst:69
msgid "*Strikethrough cloud*: The item is excluded from synchronization."
msgstr "*Scamall stríocaithe*: Tá an mhír eisiata ó shioncrónú."

#: ../../desktop/macosvfs.rst:70
msgid ""
"*Pie chart*: The item is currently being uploaded or downloaded, and the "
"progress is visualized."
msgstr ""
"*Cairt phíce*: Tá an mhír á huaslódáil nó á híoslódáil faoi láthair, agus "
"déantar an dul chun cinn a shamhlú."

#: ../../desktop/macosvfs.rst:72
msgid ""
"*Filled circle with downward arrow*: The item is available offline and will "
"be kept locally."
msgstr ""
"*Ciorcal líonta le saighead anuas*: Tá an mhír ar fáil as líne agus "
"coimeádfar go háitiúil í."

#: ../../desktop/macosvfs.rst:74
msgid "*No icon*: The item is available offline and up to date."
msgstr "*Gan deilbhín*: Tá an mhír ar fáil as líne agus cothrom le dáta."

#: ../../desktop/macosvfs.rst:77
msgid "Context menu actions"
msgstr "Comhthéacs gníomhartha roghchláir"

#: ../../desktop/macosvfs.rst:79
msgid "Screenshot of Finder with an open context menu"
msgstr "Scáileán den Aimsitheoir le roghchlár comhthéacs oscailte"

#: ../../desktop/macosvfs.rst:82
msgid ""
"The file provider extension also provides special Nextcloud features through"
" the context menu in Finder."
msgstr ""
"Cuireann síneadh an tsoláthraí comhad gnéithe speisialta Nextcloud ar fáil "
"tríd an roghchlár comhthéacs in Finder freisin."

#: ../../desktop/macosvfs.rst:86
msgid "Keep Downloaded"
msgstr "Coinnigh Íoslódáilte"

#: ../../desktop/macosvfs.rst:88
msgid ""
"Depending on the download state of a folder or file, the context menu will "
"offer to always keep an item downloaded or free up local disk space by "
"evicting the local copy while not actually deleting the item. This way, it "
"stays available any time for download from the server."
msgstr ""
"Ag brath ar staid íoslódála fillteáin nó comhaid, tairgfidh an roghchlár "
"comhthéacs mír a choinneáil íoslódáilte i gcónaí nó spás diosca áitiúil a "
"shaoradh tríd an gcóip áitiúil a dhíbirt gan an mhír a scriosadh i ndáiríre."
" Ar an mbealach seo, fanann sé ar fáil le híoslódáil ón bhfreastalaí ag am "
"ar bith."

#: ../../desktop/macosvfs.rst:94
msgid "Locking"
msgstr "Glasáil"

#: ../../desktop/macosvfs.rst:96
msgid "Screenshot of Finder showing the successful locking of a file"
msgstr "Scáileán den Finder ina bhfuil glasáil rathúil comhaid le feiceáil"

#: ../../desktop/macosvfs.rst:99
msgid ""
"If the server supports file locking, the client will offer manual locking "
"and unlocking of files in Finder."
msgstr ""
"Má thacaíonn an freastalaí le glasáil comhad, cuirfidh an cliant glasáil "
"agus díghlasáil láimhe comhad ar fáil in Finder."

#: ../../desktop/macosvfs.rst:103
msgid "Sharing"
msgstr "Roinnt"

#: ../../desktop/macosvfs.rst:105
msgid "Screenshot of Finder showing the share management"
msgstr "Scáileán den Finder a thaispeánann bainistíocht na comhroinnte"

#: ../../desktop/macosvfs.rst:108
msgid ""
"When the server supports sharing and the item is allowed to be shared, then "
"you can create new shares or manage existing shares for an item directly "
"from the context menu in Finder, as in the Nextcloud web interface."
msgstr ""
"Nuair a thacaíonn an freastalaí le comhroinnt agus nuair a cheadaítear an "
"mhír a chomhroinnt, is féidir leat comhroinnt nua a chruthú nó comhroinnt "
"atá ann cheana a bhainistiú do mhír go díreach ón roghchlár comhthéacs in "
"Finder, mar atá i gcomhéadan gréasáin Nextcloud."

#: ../../desktop/macosvfs.rst:113
msgid "File actions"
msgstr "Gníomhartha comhaid"

#: ../../desktop/macosvfs.rst:115
msgid ""
"If the server has apps installed which provide file actions for the selected"
" file types, these actions will also be available in the context menu in "
"Finder. This allows you to use server-side features of your Nextcloud "
"instance directly from the Finder."
msgstr ""
"Má tá aipeanna suiteáilte ar an bhfreastalaí a sholáthraíonn gníomhartha "
"comhaid do na cineálacha comhaid roghnaithe, beidh na gníomhartha seo ar "
"fáil sa roghchlár comhthéacs in Finder freisin. Ligeann sé seo duit gnéithe "
"taobh an fhreastalaí de d’eispéireas Nextcloud a úsáid go díreach ón Finder."

#: ../../desktop/macosvfs.rst:121
msgid "Known issues"
msgstr "Fadhbanna aitheanta"

#: ../../desktop/macosvfs.rst:124
msgid "macOS Extensions conflict"
msgstr "Coimhlint Síneadh macOS"

#: ../../desktop/macosvfs.rst:126
msgid ""
"Due to technical limitations in macOS which are imposed by Apple, it is not "
"possible to have the Finder integration for classic sync folders running in "
"parallel to an enabled virtual files integration. This means that item "
"decorations and context menu options will be unavailable for classic sync "
"folders while the file provider extension is enabled."
msgstr ""
"Mar gheall ar theorainneacha teicniúla i macOS atá curtha i bhfeidhm ag "
"Apple, ní féidir comhtháthú Finder le haghaidh fillteáin sioncrónaithe "
"clasaiceacha a bheith ag rith go comhthreomhar le comhtháthú comhad fíorúil "
"cumasaithe. Ciallaíonn sé seo nach mbeidh maisiúcháin míreanna agus roghanna"
" roghchláir chomhthéacs ar fáil le haghaidh fillteáin sioncrónaithe "
"clasaiceacha fad a bheidh síneadh an tsoláthraí comhad cumasaithe."

#: ../../desktop/macosvfs.rst:134
msgid "Alias files"
msgstr "Comhaid ainmneacha eile"

#: ../../desktop/macosvfs.rst:136
msgid ""
"When opening a macOS alias file stored on Nextcloud for the first time on a "
"device where it has not yet been downloaded, the file may open as a binary "
"document in a text editor instead of jumping to its target. This happens "
"because macOS decides how to open a file before downloading it, and alias "
"files carry no recognisable file extension or type information on the server"
" — the only way to identify them is by reading their content. Once the file "
"has been opened or downloaded once, Nextcloud Desktop learns that it is an "
"alias and stores that information locally, so all subsequent opens will work"
" correctly. To avoid the issue entirely, right-click the alias file in "
"Finder and choose **Keep Downloaded** before opening it for the first time."
msgstr ""
"Agus comhad ailias macOS atá stóráilte ar Nextcloud á oscailt den chéad uair"
" ar ghléas nár íoslódáileadh é fós air, féadfaidh an comhad oscailt mar "
"dhoiciméad dénártha in eagarthóir téacs seachas léim chuig a sprioc. "
"Tarlaíonn sé seo toisc go gcinneann macOS conas comhad a oscailt sula "
"ndéantar é a íoslódáil, agus nach mbíonn aon síneadh comhaid nó faisnéis "
"chineáil aitheanta ag comhaid ailias ar an bhfreastalaí — is é an t-aon "
"bhealach chun iad a aithint ná a n-ábhar a léamh. Nuair a bheidh an comhad "
"oscailte nó íoslódáilte uair amháin, foghlaimíonn Nextcloud Desktop gur "
"ailias é agus stórálann sé an fhaisnéis sin go háitiúil, mar sin oibreoidh "
"gach oscailt ina dhiaidh sin i gceart. Chun an fhadhb a sheachaint go "
"hiomlán, cliceáil ar dheis ar an gcomhad ailias in Finder agus roghnaigh "
"**Coinnigh Íoslódáilte** sula n-osclaítear é den chéad uair."
